videoTitle: Gen X to Gen Z: A Variety Show You've Never Seen Before!
videoDescription: Welcome to X2Z Chat! This trailer is a quick taste of what you will enjoy when you subscribe and join our community! We thrive on engagement and delighting our audience!

videoTitle: Watch out - GRENADE!! | HALO: COMBAT EVOLVED - Part 0 | Controls Training Session
videoDescription: Serge, an experienced gamer, coaches Rob, who has never played video games, on how to navigate Halo using an Xbox controller - for the very first time. Gamers:  This will bring back your memories and ecstatic feelings of picking up a controller for the very first time.  How long do you think it will take for Rob to land on his own grenade?

videoTitle: This is ADDICTING!! | HALO: COMBAT EVOLVED - Part 1 | The Pillar of Autumn
videoDescription: Serge (an experienced gamer) makes Rob (who has never played video games) beat the Pillar of Autumn level from Halo: Combat Evolved for the VERY FIRST TIME!  Join us for the ride as Rob officially begins his Halo journey! Enjoy this Halo let's play as Rob plays Halo: Combat Evolved for the first time.  Watching this, you will be able to relive the initial excitement and wonder you felt as you discovered the world of Halo for the very first time!
